<template>
    <GChart
    type="geochart"
    :data="chartData"
    :options="chartOptions"
  />
</template>
<script>
import { GChart } from "vue-google-charts";

export default {
  name: "GoogleChart",
  components: {
    GChart,
  },
  data() {
    return {
      chartData: [
      ['Country', 'Popularity'],
  ['SA', 3773870736],
  ['JO', 56090919],
  ['IL', 114142],
  ['AE', 60415],
  ['YD', 10874],
  
  ['QA', 439],
      ],

      chartOptions: {
        
  region:'145',
  datalessRegionColor:'gray',
  colorAxis:{
    colors:['#7ef9c0','#088d4f']
  },
  backgroundColor: "#799ed5",
  displayMode:'auto',
  // forceIFrame:true,
  keepAspectRatio:false
      },
    };
  },
};
</script>
